Class XML_XSLT2Processor_Error

public class XML_XSLT2Processor_Error

Error holder
This class is used as a holder for error information. It has no methods and the following properties.

Field Detail

$code

public $code

The error's code. Only populated on SAXON errors and internal error messages.

$column

public int $column

The column where the error occurred. Only populated in AltovaXML and some SAXON errors.

$file

public string $file

The filepath, or empty if the XML was loaded by libxml.

$level

public int $level

The severity of the error. For compatability with the original XSL class, one of the LIBXML_ERR_* constants is used as a value.

$line

public int $line

The line where the error occurred.

The error message.
